{
  "id": "adv_card_skr_09_02",
  "title": "川咲さくら 2話 憧れのお母さん",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_office_night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "それでは早速、勉強の成果を披露しますね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ then I’ll show you what I’ve learned!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "今から私の考える新婚生活を再現するので\n{user}さんはパートナー役をお願いします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m going to reenact my idea of newlywed life now‚\nso please play the role of my partner‚ {user}-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "随分と自信があるみたいだが\nどんな教材で勉強したんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You seem pretty confident.\nWhat kind of materials did you study?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "お母さんに話を聞いたのと、あとはシチュエーションの\n参考に、人気の漫画を読んできました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I talked to my mom‚ and I read some popular\nmanga for reference!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "すっごくおっちょこちょいの妻が奮闘する漫画です！\n遙子ちゃんいわく、十年以上続く名作だそうです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a manga about a super clumsy wife who struggles with married life!\nHaruko-chan said it’s a masterpiece that’s been running for over 10 years!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "人気ということは多くの人に\n読まれているということですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it's popular‚ that means\na lot of people read it‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "それなら、この漫画から知識を得ることで\n幸せな結婚生活を再現出来るんじゃないかと！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ if I gain knowledge from it‚\nmaybe I can recreate a happy newlywed life!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "聞いていたらどんどん不安になるんだが……\nまぁ、やってみないことには分からないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m getting more worried listening to you…\nWell‚ I guess we won’t know unless we try.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、早速やってみてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ let’s see it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.0565298399,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "任せて下さい！\n最高の花嫁を見せちゃいます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Leave it to me!\nI’ll show you the best bride ever!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "……こほん\nお帰りなさい、今日もお仕事お疲れ様です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ahem.\nWelcome home! You worked hard today!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "ご飯はこれから作りますので\n待っていて下さいね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll start making dinner now‚\nso please wait!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.3107738158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（なるほど。料理をするために）\n（事務所じゃなくてここを選んだのか）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I see. She chose this place）\n（to cook‚ instead of the office.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "ええっと、まずはお味噌汁を作って……\nその間にお肉を切らなくっちゃ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s see… First‚ make the miso soup…\nand cut the meat while that’s simmering.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "一口サイズに切ったら炒めて……\nこの次の作業は、確かメモに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Cut it into bite-sized pieces‚ then stir-fry…\nWhat was the next step again… it’s on the memo…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.5,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cooking-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1690.4695192999952,
          "startTime": 92.4666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "あったあった。塩コショウを振りかけたら\n色が変わるまで炒めて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Found it‚ found it. Sprinkle salt and pepper‚\nand stir-fry until the color changes…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cooking-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4147.407913199999,
          "startTime": 103.3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　何か忘れてるような……あああ！\nお味噌汁が吹きこぼれちゃってる！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm? I feel like I’m forgetting something… Ahhh!\nThe miso soup is boiling over!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（緊張しているのか）\n（さっきからだいぶ空回っているな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Is she nervous?）\n（She’s been pretty flustered since earlier.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "あ、危なかった……\n最後は料理をお皿によそって……完成です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That was close…\nLastly‚ plate the food… and it’s done!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、お待たせしました！\nお母さん直伝、愛情たっぷりの――わぁっ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ sorry to keep you waiting!\nMy mom’s special recipe‚ made with lots of love―― Wah?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "うわあ！？\nさ、さくら！？　大分派手に転んだな……大丈夫か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Woah?!\nS-Sakura?! You fell pretty hard… are you okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.2666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 139.6130142688
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "だ、大丈夫です。それよりごめんなさい！\n{user}さんは火傷とかしてませんか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I’m okay. But I’m so sorry!\nDid you get burned or anything‚ {user}-san?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ああ。俺も大丈夫だよ\n少し、スーツに味噌汁がかかったくらいだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh‚ yeah. I’m okay.\nJust got some miso soup on my suit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-skr017.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ！？　大変です、すぐに洗うので脱いで下さい！\nそのままじゃシミになっちゃいます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What?! This is bad! Please take it off so I can wash it right away!\nIt’ll stain if you leave it like that!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "いや、そこまで慌てなくても……\nあ、こら、待て待て、脱がそうとするんじゃない！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ you don’t have to panic that much…\nH-hey‚ wait‚ stop trying to take it off!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.5333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2344.139083499982,
          "startTime": 169.2666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-skr018.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫です！　漫画で勉強しましたから！\nちょっと待っていて下さいね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s fine! I learned how to do this from a manga!\nPlease wait a moment!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.1666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5825.749127199998,
          "startTime": 178.3333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-skr019.m4a",
      "text": "お待たせしました！\n水洗いして乾燥機に入れてきました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Here you go!\nI hand-washed it and put it in the dryer!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "乾燥機に！？\nそれだとスーツが縮んでしまうんじゃないか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The dryer?!\nWon’t the suit shrink?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-skr020.m4a",
      "text": "え！？　あー！　は、早く止めないと……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What?! Oh no! I-I have to stop it quickly…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.0494256653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-skr021.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ……手遅れでした……\nそういえば、漫画でも同じように失敗してましたね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… It’s too late…\nCome to think of it‚ they made the same mistake in the manga…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 204.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-skr022.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい、スーツもすっかり縮んでしまいましたし\n弁償させていただきます……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m so sorry. The suit has completely shrunk…\nI’ll compensate you for it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 214.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ま、まぁ気にしないでくれ。ちょっと縮んでる方が\n気持ちが引き締まる気がするよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "D-don’t worry about it. I feel like I’ll be more alert\nwith it being a little tighter.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 220.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-skr023.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ……お母さんみたいになるには、まだまだ練習が\n足りませんね。一緒にお料理の特訓もしてきたのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… I still need a lot more practice to be like Mom.\nEven though we practiced cooking together…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 229.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "漫画みたいにおっちょこちょいではあったけどな……\nでも……お母さんみたいに、か",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were clumsy like in the manga though…\nBut… like your mother…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 239.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "さくらにとって、理想のパートナーのイメージは\nお母さんみたいな人、ってことか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ your image of an ideal partner is\nsomeone like your mother‚ Sakura?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 246.32706111,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-skr024.m4a",
      "text": "……はい。私って入院が多かったんですけど\nその間、お母さんがずっと支えてくれたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes. I was hospitalized a lot‚\nand my mom always stayed by my side.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 254.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-skr025.m4a",
      "text": "不安な時は頭を撫でながら「大丈夫よ」って\n言ってくれたりなんかして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She would stroke my head and tell me‚ “It’s okay‚”\nwhenever I was feeling anxious…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 264.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-skr026.m4a",
      "text": "いつか結婚するなら、私はお母さんみたいに\n家族を優しく包める人になりたいなあって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I get married‚ I want to be someone\nwho can gently care for my family‚ like my mom.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 270.900020345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "いいお母さんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She is a wonderful mother.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 274.8307316618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-skr027.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　憧れのお母さんなんです！\nでも、ちょっと難しそうですね……あはは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! She’s my beloved mother!\nBut‚ it seems a little difficult… ahaha.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 280.7333536784,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "（なるほど。さくらは憧れのお母さんに近づきたい）\n（一心で、あんなに頑張っていたんだな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I see. Sakura was trying so hard because）\n（she wanted to be like her mom.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 290.5333536784,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "さくら、そんなに気にするな。今回はちょっと空回って\nしまっただけで、相手のために行動した結果だろう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't worry too much about it‚ Sakura. This time you just\ngot a little flustered. You were just trying to be nice‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 298.300020345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "何もマイナスに考える必要はないと思うぞ\nむしろこれから練習していけばいい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don’t have to think about it negatively.\nYou can just practice from now on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 305.800020345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-skr028.m4a",
      "text": "そうでしょうか……？\nでも、撮影までに出来るようにならないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really…?\nBut I need to be able to do it by the shoot…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 311.300020345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "相手のために不慣れなことを一生懸命やるパートナーは\n魅力的なものだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A partner who tries their best to do something unfamiliar‚\nfor their partner‚ is very charming.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 319.0333536784,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "だから、今のさくらのままで撮影に臨んでも\nいいと思うけどな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ I think it's fine to go into the shoot\njust as you are now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 324.300020345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-skr029.m4a",
      "text": "今のままの私で、一生懸命に……\nありがとうございます、ちょっと自信がわいてきました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just as I am now‚ and try my best…\nThank you. I feel a little more confident now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 330.9333536784,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-skr030.m4a",
      "text": "では、最後にもう一度だけ挑戦させて下さい\n完璧には出来なくても、一生懸命頑張りたいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ let me try one last time.\nEven if I can’t do it perfectly‚ I want to give it my all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 340.2666870117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-koh019.m4a",
      "text": "最後と言わず、本番まで何度でも付き合うよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t say it’s the last time.I’ll join you as many times as you want until the shoot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 345.2494157786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-skr031.m4a",
      "text": "言いましたね！　では撮影本番まで\n毎日私の特訓に付き合ってもらいますよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You promised! Then‚ until the actual shoot‚\nI’ll have you help me practice every day!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 353.8333536784,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-skr032.m4a",
      "text": "私も決して手は抜きませんので\n{user}さんもよろしくお願いしますね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I won’t go easy on you either‚\nso please do your best too‚ {user}-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 360.4666870117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_02-koh020.m4a",
      "text": "お、お手柔らかにな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "G-go easy on me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 363.9330215448,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}